"A pair of leather gloves with no fingers, allowing greater manual dexterity."
msgstr "一副無指皮手套，能提供更好的手部靈活性。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "pair of armored fingerless gloves"
msgid_plural "pairs of armored fingerless gloves"
