"A pair of leather gloves with no fingers, allowing greater manual dexterity."
"  These have been crudely reinforced with steel guards across the back."
msgstr "一雙無指皮手套，提供更高的手部靈活性。其手背部分已用鋼製護板粗糙加固。"

